35e8220c601aca620da1cfcb978c8b7a64dcbf15.query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS fills (
            id numeric PRIMARY KEY,
            time timestamptz not null,
            market text not null,
            open_orders text not null,
            open_orders_owner text not null,
            bid bool not null,
            maker bool not null,
            native_qty_paid numeric not null,
            native_qty_received numeric not null,
            native_fee_or_rebate numeric not null,
            fee_tier text not null,
            order_id text not null
        )

4bab7d4329b2969b2ba610546c660207740c9baf.query: CREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS idx_id_market ON fills (id, market)

6658c0121e5a7defbd1fe7c549ca0a957b188b9e.query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS candles (
            id serial,
            market_name text,
            start_time timestamptz,
            end_time timestamptz,
            resolution text,
            open numeric,
            close numeric,
            high numeric,
            low numeric,
            volume numeric,
            complete bool
        )

817ee7903cb5095f85fb787beff04ace3a452cf8.query: CREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS idx_market_time ON fills (market, time)

866773102b03b002e9d0535d3173f36264e1d30a.query:
SELECT 
        start_time as "start_time!",
        end_time as "end_time!",
        resolution as "resolution!",
        market_name as "market_name!",
        open as "open!",
        close as "close!",
        high as "high!",
        low as "low!",
        volume as "volume!",
        complete as "complete!"
        from candles
        where market_name = $1
        and resolution = $2
        and start_time >= $3
        and end_time <= $4
        ORDER BY start_time asc

b71ec8e5c041cec2c83778f31f7dc723cc1b5a8b.query:
SELECT 
         time as "time!",
         bid as "bid!",
         maker as "maker!",
         native_qty_paid as "native_qty_paid!",
         native_qty_received as "native_qty_received!",
         native_fee_or_rebate as "native_fee_or_rebate!" 
         from fills 
         where market = $1
         and time >= $2
         and time < $3 
         and maker = true
         ORDER BY time asc

dc367af7bb8da9d57033833da06567f3f3cfdcff.query:
SELECT 
        open_orders_owner, 
        sum(
          native_qty_paid * CASE bid WHEN true THEN 0 WHEN false THEN 1 END
        ) as "raw_ask_size!",
        sum(
          native_qty_received * CASE bid WHEN true THEN 1 WHEN false THEN 0 END
        ) as "raw_bid_size!"
      FROM public."fills"
 WHERE  market = $1
        AND time >= $2
        AND time < $3
 GROUP  BY open_orders_owner
 ORDER  BY 
    sum(native_qty_paid * CASE bid WHEN true THEN 0 WHEN false THEN 1 END) 
    + 
    sum(native_qty_received * CASE bid WHEN true THEN 1 WHEN false THEN 0 END) 
DESC
